Hades is a Matlab toolbox for MEG and EEG analysis that is being developed by Cristina Campi, Annalisa Pascarella, Michele Piana and Alberto Sorrentino at the Dipartimento di Matematica, Universita' degli Studi di Genova.

Caution: Hades is a toolbox written and released for neuroimaging research purposes only with no guarantee of suitability for any particular purpose. Hades, or data obtained from Hades, should not under any circumstances be used for clinical purposes.

For more information please visit http://hades.dima.unige.it
Report a bug or contribute a coding suggestion to hades@dima.unige.it

